<subSubSection pageId="126" pageNumber="885" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="126.[1405,2613,1949,2847]" pageId="126" pageNumber="885">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1407,1760,2656,2689]" pageId="126" pageNumber="885">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Virtually nothing is known regarding ecology and threats of Sody’s Yellow Bat. It is apparently common in some parts of Borneo.
</paragraph>
